videos.headline: Tony Bradley with a strong block than sends the ball flying to the sideline

videos.description: North Carolina's Justin Jackson knocks down 3-pointers in back-to-back possessions against Monmouth, giving him five makes from deep with six minutes left in the first half.
videos.headline: UNC's Justin Jackson on fire from deep in first half
Justin Robinson drains a jumper and draws a foul

videos.headline: Monmouth's Micah Seaborn hits a half court shot to beat the buzzer at the end of the first half

videos.description: North Carolina's Justin Jackson hits six 3-pointers and scores 28 points in the No. 9 Tar Heels' 102-74 win against Monmouth.
videos.headline: Jackson's 28 fuels UNC past Monmouth
